name: Keys to the Past WSEI Game Jam
name_original: Keys to the Past WSEI Game Jam
description:
Keys to the Past

Game for a 20-hour, 7th WSEI game jam with a "nostalgia" theme.

You are a princess who, after years, managed to leave her chamber in a high tower. The castle that was her home stands empty... What happened here? Why and where has everyone gone? 

The princess, searching for answers, tours the castle recalling her childhood spent among the castle walls.

~~
